{"tid":871473,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"48歲李嘉欣曬自拍 白髮蒼蒼臉頰凹陷網崩潰認不出","createTime":"2018-10-22T03:19:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T14:22:19.000Z","uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"12aa25a8f7ee287a6bf4709e35f860b82b2a5e5e","tid":871473,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:19:05.000Z","msg":"48歲混血港星李嘉欣五官深邃美豔，1988年參加香港小姐競選，獲冠軍殊榮，有「最美港姐」封號，近日曬自拍向粉絲問安，疑因P圖下手過重，她的臉頰嚴重凹陷，甚至還有些變形，讓不少網友乍看認不出。<br />\n李嘉欣16日在微博分享新照，留言詢問粉絲「你今天開心嗎？」唯美自拍照竟讓網友認不出，她的眼睛被指太大、下巴過尖，臉頰明顯凹陷，臉部有些許變形，認為P圖手法過於拙劣，崩潰直呼：「這張不像妳了！」、「P過頭了」、「變形了」、「哈哈哈女神不會自拍呀！」此外，李嘉欣在頭上加了5顆不同顏色的愛心貼圖，恰好遮住白髮，此舉讓粉絲不禁感「這是有白頭髮了嗎？」、「原來女神也會老！」、「我真係恭喜你呀！」、「怪唔之得開公司捧洪欣都唔捧你啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0cqFVnb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0cqFVnb.jpg&h=7e265334&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"339f0ac5a6f025c73061759a6d92a65b74ff772f","tid":871473,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:36:12.000Z","msg":"好靚"},{"pid":"7cc0f190b24d032281a9b2038be4f2a06223dfcd","tid":871473,"uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:40:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好靚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52tL6Bo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52tL6Bo.jpg&h=7ab29c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe5c2c8d5e183bcb5b29123a56ae22f083785fd","tid":871473,"uid":4285,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:41:46.000Z","msg":"始終都係一個閪女人"},{"pid":"ba1fc8872c33ae6b2e04f412ceeb12d8f10f8366","tid":871473,"uid":12033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"幾靚都好 閪格都變柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"